sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bfa6acb6be45d22a984972d1ecb86e1f2637e8","tid":119882,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成班都冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兜咪比咗柱間細胞救佐助囉</blockquote><br />\n咁點解另外果隻眼唔變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會變唔係因為得到柱間細胞，而係得到亞修羅（定唔知因陀羅其中一個）嘅力量<br />\n佐助有一隻眼開到就係因為六道仙人比左果份力量佢<br />\n至於點解只變一隻我覺得純粹係造型因素<br />\n始終雙色眼型好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係紅藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎造型<br />\n二黎歷代開輪迴眼既人都只有一隻眼係有勾玉<br />\n斑同老母都係額頭開,你唔會想佐助係額頭開隻眼掛"},{"pid":"4a298f4f409790b6135deebfb587143f83ee31d1","tid":119882,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成班都冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兜咪比咗柱間細胞救佐助囉</blockquote><br />\n咁點解另外果隻眼唔變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會變唔係因為得到柱間細胞，而係得到亞修羅（定唔知因陀羅其中一個）嘅力量<br />\n佐助有一隻眼開到就係因為六道仙人比左果份力量佢<br />\n至於點解只變一隻我覺得純粹係造型因素<br />\n始終雙色眼型好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係紅藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎造型<br />\n二黎歷代開輪迴眼既人都只有一隻眼係有勾玉<br />\n斑同老母都係額頭開,你唔會想佐助係額頭開隻眼掛</blockquote><br />\n隻勾玉輪迴眼開喺額頭真係諗下都笑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過開頭我以為佐助開到一隻輪迴眼係因為有開輪迴眼嘅條件（瀕死+柱間細胞）"},{"pid":"7e237512b944fc40803766feaddaee1d89274314","tid":119882,"uid":73728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成班都冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兜咪比咗柱間細胞救佐助囉</blockquote><br />\n咁點解另外果隻眼唔變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會變唔係因為得到柱間細胞，而係得到亞修羅（定唔知因陀羅其中一個）嘅力量<br />\n佐助有一隻眼開到就係因為六道仙人比左果份力量佢<br />\n至於點解只變一隻我覺得純粹係造型因素<br />\n始終雙色眼型好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係紅藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一黎造型<br />\n二黎歷代開輪迴眼既人都只有一隻眼係有勾玉<br />\n斑同老母都係額頭開,你唔會想佐助係額頭開隻眼掛</blockquote><br />\n隻勾玉輪迴眼開喺額頭真係諗下都笑到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過開頭我以為佐助開到一隻輪迴眼係因為有開輪迴眼嘅條件（瀕死+柱間細胞）</blockquote><br />\n依家一隻眼黑色一隻眼輪回好樣衰"}]}